{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_52_03",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 3話 サーターアンダギー！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "えぇと……地図を見た感じだと、この近くに\nサーターアンダギー屋さんがあるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's see… looking at the map‚ it seems\nthere's a sata andagi shop around here",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐもうすぐ～……って、あれ？\n電信柱に張り紙が……「猫を探してます」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Almost there‚ almost there… Huh?\nThere's a poster on the telephone pole…\"Looking for a Cat.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん。猫ちゃんの特徴、見て？\n白い毛並みに鈴の付いた首輪……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san. Look at the cat's description?\nWhite fur and a collar with a bell…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12400.0000001,
          "startTime": 37.0333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.2333330791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの猫ちゃんも……鈴の付いた首輪を付けてた！\nまだ遠くに行ってないかも。芽衣、探して来る！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That kitty from earlier… also had a collar with a bell!\nIt might not have gone far yet. Mei will go look for it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、おい、芽衣！？　探すってどこを……って\nもう行ってしまった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ hey‚ Mei!? Where are you going to look…\nShe's already gone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3766.668192600001,
          "startTime": 47.5666681926
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3751.4182250000017,
          "startTime": 47.551418225
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8233.333333300003,
          "startTime": 52.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.3166681926
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.3166681926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣！　こんな所にいたのか……って、あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei! You were here… huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3666681926,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8394.130960999995,
          "startTime": 56.7607991536
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.4607988994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "よーしよしよし、お利口さんだねー\nもう大丈夫だよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good‚ good‚ good‚ you're a good kitty~\nIt's okay now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1274658203,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bell-04.m4a",
          "delay": 5315.250221800006,
          "startTime": 58.7760491212
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.2941322327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "凄いな、芽衣は。まさか本当に見つけるとは\nしかもこんなに早く……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're amazing‚ Mei. I never thought you'd actually find it.\nAnd so quickly too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4607991536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.827465566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "近くにいた猫ちゃんに聞いたら教えてくれたんだよー\nあっちのビーチの方にいるよ～って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I asked a nearby kitty and it told meー\n\"it's over there by the beach\"~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8256696065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.9941322327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さすが日頃から猫の集会に参加してるだけはあるな\nでも、急に飛び出して行くから心配したぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Impressive— that's what regular cat gathering attendance gets you.\nBut I was worried when you suddenly ran off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.094132487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい。この子が迷子になってると思ったら\n心配でいてもたってもいられなくなっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. When I thought this kitty was lost‚\nI was so worried I couldn't just sit still…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1274658203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.860787201
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ飼い主さんの所に……って、あー！\n連絡先も住所も見てなかった！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let's take it back to its owner… Ah!\nI didn't look at the contact information or the address!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8607991536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.260787201
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、そんなこともあろうかと張り紙の写真を\n撮っておいたから。まずはこの番号に連絡しようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's alright. I thought this might happen‚ so I took\na photo of the poster. Shall we contact this number first?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9607991536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.0274523418
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……ありがと\n……ほんと頼りになるなぁ、えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san… Thank you.\n…You're really reliable‚ ehehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.4607976277,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.66666669999,
          "startTime": 116.7274642944
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.1274642944
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.1274642944
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん～、まさか猫ちゃんがこーんなに沢山の\nサーターアンダギーになるなんて思わなかったよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe~ I never thought the kitty\nwould become so many sata andagi~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2274734497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.3274620057
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "あむっ……もぐもぐ……んー美味しい！！\n揚げたて最高！　{user}さんも食べる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Amu… munch munch… mmm‚ delicious!!\nFresh fried is the best! {user}-san‚ want some?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0941309611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.5274559022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、両手が塞がってるし大丈夫だ。それから、正確\nには猫がサーターアンダギーになった訳じゃないぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nah‚ my hands are full‚ so I'm good. Also‚ to be precise‚\nthe cat didn't actually become sata andagi‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.1274642944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "それくらい、芽衣も分かってるよ～！\nでも、びっくりだったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ Mei knows that much~!\nBut it was surprising‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.3941309611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.8941378276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "猫ちゃんの飼い主さんが、行こうとしてたサーター\nアンダギー屋さんのおばあちゃんだったなんて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The cat's owner turned out to be the grandma from\nthe sata andagi shop we were going to!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9608118693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.0608024597
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "こんな偶然あるんだね。でも、猫ちゃん連れて帰った時\n……お店のおばあちゃん、本当に嬉しそうだったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Such a coincidence. But‚ when we brought the kitty back‚\n…the grandma at the shop looked really happy‚ didn't she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.660810852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_03-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ心配してた、ってことだよね\n見つかってほんとに良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That means she was that worried about it‚ right?\nI'm really glad we found it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.3941441853,
